  "name": "Return Reasons",
  "body": "<h1 data-id=\"return-reasons\">Return Reasons</h1>\n<p>This feature allows you to create and configure custom reasons for product returns. Staff will be able to select the reason when process a return or exchange. View more details in the <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://galaxy.maropost.com/s/article/1Return-Reason-Report\">Return Reason</a> report. </p>\n<p>To configure your Return Reasons:</p>\n<ol><li>Navigate to <strong>Settings &gt; Return Reasons</strong></li><li>Enter the <strong>Return Reason </strong>name<br/><img alt=\"mceclip0 - 2023-07-09T231804.646.png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000pphaEEAQ.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000pphaEEAQ.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000pphaEEAQ.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000pphaEEAQ.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000pphaEEAQ.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000pphaEEAQ.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000pphaEEAQ.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000pphaEEAQ.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></li><li>Tick <strong>Enabled</strong></li><li>Click <strong>Insert</strong></li><li>Use the <strong>pencil</strong> icon to edit the name for an existing Reason</li><li>Click the <strong>trash can </strong>icon to delete Return Reasons (you will be unable to delete the Return Reason if it's already been used for a sale)</li></ol>",
